13 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 28 O.S. 2021, Section 152, as
14 amended by Section 1, Chapter 237, O.S.L. 2022 (28 O.S. Supp. 2024,
15 Section 152), is amended to read as follows:
16 Section 152. A. In any civil case filed in a district court,
17 the court clerk shall collect, at the time of filing, the following
18 flat fees, none of which shall ever be refundable, and which shall
19 be the only charge for court costs, except as is otherwise
20 specifically provided for by law:
21 1. Actions for divorce, alimony without divorce,
22 separate maintenance, custody or support......................$183.00
23 2. Any ancillary proceeding to modify or vacate
24 a divorce decree providing for custody or support..............$43.00
